id: 151
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"I’m binding the concept to a dark luxury system: charcoal background, white logo treatment, oyster-shell surfaces, muted silver copy, and a restrained whisky/bronze accent. The page rhythm will be home, menus, functions, and contact/booking, with the existing booking and voucher intent carried through."}

